name: Flippy Hand-drawn Type
description:
Flippy is a mixed bag of uppercase and lowercase lettering to be used for the hand-crafted look. Not all glyphs or numbers are used with this set, it's mainly the initial alphabet. Unlimited and infinite licensing on this typeface. Feel free to morph, change, use on the Web, anything!
Digital download will be sent to your PayPal e-mail address within 24 hours. If you would like it sent to another e-mail address, please supply that in the comments

name: Charles Gnarly Hand-drawn Type
description:
This hand-drawn type features some modern styling with some old classic sketch feel. A small mixture of upper and lowercase lettering. Emphasis on the Q, M, N, and W make this type unique. Not all glyphs or numbers are used with this set, it's mainly the initial alphabet. Unlimited and infinite licensing on this typeface. Feel free to morph, change, use on the Web, anything!
Digital download will be sent to your PayPal e-mail address within 24 hours. If you would like it sent to another e-mail address, please supply that in the comments

name: Smiley Booklet
description: Digital print on thick Kraft paper, this hand-crafted 8+ page booklet features all original artwork with the "smiley face" theme. The idea is to remember that smiling with eventually make everything in your life better. Limited run of 50. Shipping is in a heavy Kraft stay-flat mailer sure not to bend. Free goodies inside each order. Signature of authenticity and run number on the back of each booklet.

name: Client Rants
description: A collection of thoughts and rants over the past 5 years. Not necessarily due to clients, more work situations. But still. Printed on Kraft paper this legal letter size print 9.5" x 11" is the perfect cost-effective solution for giving every designer in your office a good laugh. Great to look at while dealing with tough times. It's nice to remember we all go through the same shit. This is not a limited print, all shipping comes in a Kraft stay-flat mailer with extra goodies. Every print numbered and signed.

name: Grow Deck
description: Each deck comes signed and numbered on the top (where grip goes), and comes with a small piece of fishing line in case you would like to hang the deck on your wall (instructions included). A lime green and navy compilation of organic matter, your organic urban lifestyle shred stick. I realize the price for this deck is quite high, each deck will be custom made for your order. Meaning, I am only putting the deck into production after you order it. The 1 to 1 level of this makes production costs high. Shipping included in price. Thank you for all your love and support.
